# One target per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# INTERNAL mode — IPs, ranges, or CIDRs only (hostnames are rejected):
#   10.10.10.0/24
#   192.168.50.10-50
#   172.16.1.5
#
# EXTERNAL mode — public IPs / ranges / CIDRs, and/or root domains.
# Root domains are expanded to subdomains -> resolved public IPs by phase 02:
#   203.0.113.10
#   203.0.113.0/24
#   198.51.100.10-50
#   example.com
#   example.org
